---
import Button from './Button.astro';
---

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-badge">About Biomentis.ai</div>
    
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <h2 class="about-title">
          Empowering Life Science
          <span class="highlight">with AI</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="about-description">
From foundational understanding to hands-on experience, we guide your professionals through the world of applied AI.        </p>
</p>        
        <p class="about-description">
We’re professors and practitioners in AI and the life sciences. We know both sides and how to connect them.
</p>        

        <p class="about-description">
Whether you're in pharma, biotech, medtech, or any research-intensive industry, we shape content around your challenges.
</p>        

        <p class="about-description">
Our support doesn’t stop after the workshop. We stick with you to build, validate, and implement real-world AI solutions.        </p>
</p>        
        
        <div class="about-cta">
          <Button href="#services" variant="outline">Learn More About Our Services</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/images/about-image.jpg" alt="Our team at work" />
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: var(--light-bg);
  }

  .about-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
    color: var(--secondary-color);
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--secondary-color);
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    display: block;
  }

  .about-description {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-color);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-cta {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .about-image {
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--text-color);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .about-description {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .about-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
